Backend Project (FastAPI)

This repository contains a backend application developed using FastAPI.
The project is designed to simulate a SaaS-based system with features such as user management, authentication, project handling, subscriptions, payments, and notifications.



Overview

The application provides a structured backend system with the following capabilities:

- User registration and login with OTP verification
- Secure authentication using JWT tokens
- Role-based access control (Admin and User)
- Project and task management
- Subscription system (Free and Pro plans)
- Payment handling using Stripe
- Notification system for user updates
- Admin dashboard for monitoring platform activity



Key Features

User Module

- Register new users
- OTP-based account verification
- Login with secure password hashing
- View user profile



Project & Task Module

- Create, update, delete projects
- Each user can manage their own projects
- Free users are limited to 3 projects
- Pro users have no limit
- Tasks can be created under each project



Subscription Module

- Default plan assigned during registration (Free plan)
- Upgrade to Pro plan via payment
- Subscription details stored and managed in database



Payment Integration

- Stripe Checkout integration
- Payment success handling
- Payment details stored in database



Notification System

- Notifications created for important actions such as:
  - Payment success
  - Admin messages
- Users can view and manage notifications



Admin Module

- View all users
- Activate / deactivate users
- View subscriptions and payments
- View platform analytics:
  - Total users
  - Total projects
  - Total revenue



Technology Stack

- FastAPI
- SQLAlchemy
- MySQL
- Alembic
- JWT Authentication
- Stripe API



